title: Cinematic Magic LED Light Message Box
description:
About products:-

Cinematic Custom Message LED LIGHTBOX
LED Home Décor Large Light Box with 109 Letters and Characters, Wall Mounted or Tabletop, Battery or USB Powered, White.
Home delivery all over Nepal. Call us or send us a message to confirm the order or to know more.
VINTAGE LIGHTBOX: is designed to look like those retro cinema signs that advertise a movie and share a fun message. You can now write your fun, inspirational or motivational message on the lightbox
MORE LETTERS & CHARACTERS: Thanks to the 109 letters and characters, your options are endless. Be creative and change the message on the lightbox as often as you want! It is fast and effortless
DECORATE ANY SPACE: with the cinema lightbox for any occasion. You can use the lightbox for parties and gatherings. Thanks to the extra-long durable USB cable, it won’t be hard to find the perfect spot
EASY PLACEMENT: The lightbox can be wall-mounted, or freestanding. Place strategically and spread humor, good vibes, and laughter.
USB powered (white USB cable included) or battery-operated (6xAA not included)
